Mirror, mirror on the wall,
Who is the fairest of them all?

Fans of the Lunar Chronicles know Queen Levana as a ruler who uses her “glamour” to gain power. But long before she crossed paths with Cinder, Scarlet, and Cress, Levana lived a very different story – a story that has never been told . . . until now.', NULL, 2015, '841835996X', '9788418359965', 272, NULL, NULL, 'https://covers.openlibrary.org/b/id/9885060-L.jpg', '/works/OL20779152W', NULL, 'Sep 26, 2022', 'English', NULL, 1, 0, 'fairest-the-lunar-chronicles-marissa-meyer', 0, NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 'public', '2026-03-16 15:02:58', '2026-03-24 23:24:42');
